org.apache.poi.poifs.crypt.temp

Class EncryptedTempData

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.poi.poifs.crypt.temp.EncryptedTempData

  • @Beta
public class EncryptedTempData
extends java.lang.Object
    EncryptedTempData can be used to buffer binary data in a secure way, by using encrypted temp files.(CryptedTempData可用于通过使用加密的临时文件以安全的方式缓冲二进制数据。)

      • getOutputStream

        public java.io.OutputStream getOutputStream()
                                     throws java.io.IOException
        Returns the output stream for writing the data.

        Make sure to close it, otherwise the last cipher block is not written completely.

        (返回写入数据的输出流。确保关闭它，否则最后一个密码块不会被完全写入。)
        Returns:
        the outputstream(产出流)
        Throws:
